 What is Helm ?
 &lt;a href="#what-is-helm-" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink to this heading">ðŸ”—&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Helm is a Package Manager for Kubernetes, it allows defining, installing, upgrading and deleting applications.&lt;br>
A Helm Chart is an application packaged with Helm, it has a script file/folder structure and uses a templating language.&lt;br>
The Helm Client is a binary used to manipulate application packaged with Helm.&lt;/p>
